  <h2>Mademoiselle Caroline Rivi&#232;re</h2>

  <p><small>by <a href="#">Jean-Auguste-Dominique Ingres</a></small></p>

  <a href="images/painting1_large.jpg">
    <img src="images/painting1_medium.jpg" alt="Portrait of Mademoiselle Caroline Rivi&#232;re by Jean Auguste Dominique Ingres" title="Portrait of Mademoiselle Caroline Rivi&#232;re by Jean Auguste Dominique Ingres" hspace="30px">
  </a>

  <p>The portrait of Mademoiselle Caroline Rivi&#232;re was painted in 1806 by the French Neoclassical artist Jean Auguste Dominique Ingres, and today hangs in the Louvre. It is the third of three portraits of the Rivi&#232;re family the artist painted that year.</p>
  <p>
    Date: <em>1806</em>
    <br>Medium: <em>Oil on Canvas</em>
    <br>Dimensions: <em>100 x 70cm</em>
    <br>Home: <em>Mus&#232;e du Louvre, Paris</em>
  </p>

